islike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"e3cffb2625336e2db7aedc42a14de3afdbaeeef0","tid":2198483,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"f7e18ddc679b506f5f9fa44f1a35a121351d86bd","tid":2198483,"uid":57,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"659bd1842c63e4f8517d81def888c3db1947a1b5","tid":2198483,"uid":281823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d8B1LNrBpqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd8B1LNrBpqc&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=b611dde4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d8B1LNrBpqc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tS0dl8KEbng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtS0dl8KEbng&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=28ec8f89\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tS0dl8KEbng</a><br />\n<br />\n到時Xbox出黎做到呢個效果我裸跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"即係乜嘢效果？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"可以load勁多asset<br />\n過場完全無難度 例如Unreal條片 7:45"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"你代佢答定未轉acc?"},{"pid":"0cf612d19fc2aa93ccaad4693942a1a693064aa4","tid":2198483,"uid":109923,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"有咩效果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講啲唔講啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nUE5 Nanite只可以render static mesh &amp; 非透明嘅嘢，植被、布料、毛髮、體積雲，呢啲會郁嘅或者有透明部份嘅都用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遊戲角色會郁都係用唔著，所以成條demo得啲砂石同金屬，再加一個泥膠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞奇與叮噹你係咪想講00:50嗰度？<br />\n個傳送點唔係玩家自由決定飛去邊到，由玩家未跳落去嗰時已經可以預先stream好晒下一張地圖啲資源，呢個亦都係所有無loading遊戲好普遍嘅做法。就算由起跳計起，前前後後都用咗4秒實時演算做過渡，一個普通ssd都做到嘅事...<br />\n<br />\n要吹奏嘅話，呢條片0.8秒load完蜘蛛俠地圖仲勁啦，加返無縫過渡更完美，你真係豬隊友嚟嫁喎...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1130645990627631105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1130645990627631105&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=dca79c43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1130645990627631105&h=8527e5f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1130645990627631105</a><br />\n<br />\n高速SSD可以減少幾多遊戲載入時間唔係重點，fresh start隻game同普通SSD差距好少，stream地圖資源係睇隨機讀寫，連續讀取對打機冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n可以減少gameplay/地圖設計被storage I/O限制先至係重點，好多gameplay&amp;地圖設計都受影響：<br />\n線性/非線性（可否預判stream定啲資源）<br />\n視角移動速度（包括人物、工具移動速度）<br />\n地圖設計（山谷、盤地、空氣牆、過場等等自然或障礙物分隔，拖慢移動速度、減少要stream嘅資源）<br />\n<br />\n然而一個open world非線性自由探索嘅遊戲，一隻普通ssd都夠做，再上已經係特殊gameplay先需要。如果整隻超能力game或者飛坐火箭自由飛，速度係條片嘅片尾咁就真係影響到gameplay啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係咁快嘅速度仲有冇可操作性？<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1130645990627631105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1130645990627631105&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=dca79c43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1130645990627631105&h=8527e5f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1130645990627631105</a><br />\n<br />\n以目前遊戲嘅設計，PS5 SSD最有用都只係遠距瞬間移動時會load快少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e880bc919efa0739b2ae477ffa2465c8f1d7a02","tid":2198483,"uid":13958,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"勁係勁<br />\n但如果淨係得PS5 做到<br />\n好難說服d 大廠設計咁既關卡<br />\n始終多平台賣多幾份先係優先<br />\n唔通你PS版係即時演算<br />\nXbox 版就入黑畫面過場咩<br />\n呢d 獨特功能最後又係獨佔game 先有份"},{"pid":"7f90a0adb80a04740a04c8a8eae536e9476ec61b","tid":2198483,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n瑞奇與叮噹你係咪想講04:16嗰度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你條片係04:16先啱<br />\n<br />\n其實隻game喺04:05已經stream緊下一張地圖嘅資源<br />\n04:16喺地面滑行已經load緊下一張地圖，清除返上一張地圖嘅資源<br />\n你以為04:21開傳送裂縫先開始load？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93853ca5b97587e769e1ba1cadab2d200a984177","tid":2198483,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"剩係想知幾錢同日期<br />\n佢用咩都冇所謂<br />\n點都要買"},{"pid":"6fc0cf79e07dabc3055df6aeaaa1a3aa020b335e","tid":2198483,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f90a0adb80a04740a04c8a8eae536e9476ec61b","tid":2198483,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n瑞奇與叮噹你係咪想講04:16嗰度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你條片係04:16先啱<br />\n<br />\n其實隻game喺04:05已經stream緊下一張地圖嘅資源<br />\n04:16喺地面滑行已經load緊下一張地圖，清除返上一張地圖嘅資源<br />\n你以為04:21開傳送裂縫先開始load？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"仲有，成16GB display ram。load 完放係buffering其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d01300811f9de214f4a15edc7bb03a47a1ee6b6","tid":2198483,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6fc0cf79e07dabc3055df6aeaaa1a3aa020b335e","tid":2198483,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f90a0adb80a04740a04c8a8eae536e9476ec61b","tid":2198483,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n瑞奇與叮噹你係咪想講04:16嗰度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你條片係04:16先啱<br />\n<br />\n其實隻game喺04:05已經stream緊下一張地圖嘅資源<br />\n04:16喺地面滑行已經load緊下一張地圖，清除返上一張地圖嘅資源<br />\n你以為04:21開傳送裂縫先開始load？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"仲有，成16GB display ram。load 完放係buffering其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 